        public void create(java.lang.String cineplexName,
                   java.lang.String code,
                   CinemaType cinemaType,
                   SeatingPlan seatingPlan)
        CREATE a new Cinema and add it into the database file Attributes are validated before creation If attributes are not allowed, throw error and do nothing If Database file exist, existing records are read and new Cinema object is aopended before saving If Database file does not exist, Cinema object will be written to a new file and saved
        Parameters:
        cineplexName - Name of Cineplex that this Cinema will be added to
        code - This cinema's code
        cinemaType - This cinema's type
        seatingPlan - This cinema's seating plan
